:SCREEN INTRO
TEXTONLY,"The Urban Game",0,5,100,0,C||28|B|255-0-0
TEXTONLY, "You have been put in charge of a city in decline. Population",20,20,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "is falling, unemployment is high and rising, housing for the",20,25,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "poor is still inadequate.  Your challenge is to find programs",20,30,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "that can turn this city around.  You are free to decide what you",20,35,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "want to accomplish - growth, improved economic well being or",20,40,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "whatever you wish.  You will be given a few levers in the form",20,45,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "of job training, housing and business development programs.  Use",20,50,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "these to accomplish your goals.  You have 150 years, and you",20,55,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "can make a decision every 5 years.",20,60,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "You do not need to finish the 150 years, and there is no scorekeeping.",20,70,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "The purpose of the game is to see if your actions have their intended",20,75,100,0,L
TEXTONLY, "effect, and attempt to understand why they work, or fail.",20,80,100,0,L
BUTTON,"Press any key or click to continue.",50,90,30,0,C,,,MAIN
ANYKEY,"",0,0,0,0,0,,,MAIN

:SCREEN MAIN
TEXTONLY,"The Urban Game - Main Menu",0,5,100,0,C||28|B|255-0-0
!RECTANGLE,"",4,19,45,22,C 4
BUTTON,"Go back to the introductory material",50,20,40,0,C,GgIi,,INTRO
BUTTON,"Play the game",50,25,40,0,C,Pp,SIMULATE>RUNNAME|?Name for new game output (NOT BASE or BASE100!!!),STARTGAME
BUTTON,"Continue with a previous game",50,30,40,0,C,Cc,SIMULATE>RUNNAME|?Name of game to continue|E,STARTGAME2
BUTTON,"Analyze game results",50,35,40,0,C,Aa,,ANALYZE
BUTTON,"Exit to model selection menu",50,40,40,0,C,EeXx,SPECIAL>LOADMODEL|..\intro.vmf&SPECIAL>LOADAPPINT|intro.vcd@3,
LINE,"",0,45,100,0
TEXTONLY,"Instructions and Comments - If Necessary use the scroll bar to see everything",0,55,100,0,C 3
